	measure 'Antal Churn Kunder Nuuday Current' = ```
			
			VAR StartDate = MIN ( 'Calendar'[Date] )
			VAR EndDate   = MAX ( 'Calendar'[Date] )
			VAR AsOf      = EndDate
			RETURN
			CALCULATE (
			    DISTINCTCOUNT ( AltiboxMobil_Nuuday[Mobil nummer] ),
			    
			    REMOVEFILTERS ( 'Calendar Comparison' ),
			    REMOVEFILTERS ( AltiboxMobil_Nuuday[FromDate] ),
			
			    USERELATIONSHIP ( 'Calendar'[Date], AltiboxMobil_Nuuday[Udporteringsdato] ),
			
			    DATEVALUE ( AltiboxMobil_Nuuday[Udporteringsdato])>= StartDate,
			    DATEVALUE ( AltiboxMobil_Nuuday[Udporteringsdato] ) <= EndDate,
			
			    AltiboxMobil_Nuuday[FromDate] <= AsOf,
			    COALESCE ( AltiboxMobil_Nuuday[ToDate], DATE ( 9999, 12, 31 ) ) >= AsOf,
			
			    AltiboxMobil_Nuuday[Status] = "Nedlagt")
			```
		formatString: #,0
		displayFolder: Nuuday
		lineageTag: bcdcd3bc-101f-4ef3-85a1-3ed1705e7d21

		changedProperty = DisplayFolder

		changedProperty = Name

		changedProperty = FormatString

